                                        <p>The budget was prepared in Ghana Cedi, hence, the grand total estimated for the proposed project budget is GH¢ 244,467.21 which is equivalent to $ 45,694.80. It is based on the current economic trend and it is subject to Change. The Rehabilitation of a community dugout and the construction of a Rain Water harvest in a school for sustainable water in needy areas in Laligu, Northern Ghana.</p>
